wdi2-SH.XPD.EHEX.PC.CD.def: Current external expenditures on health per capita expressed in current US dollars. External sources are composed of direct foreign transfers and foreign transfers distributed by government encompassing all financial inflows into the national health system from outside the country.
wdi2-SH.XPD.EHEX.PC.CD.name: External health expenditure per capita
wdi2-SH.XPD.EHEX.PC.CD.source: World Health Organization Global Health Expenditure database (http://apps.who.int/nha/database).
